    <defName>SalarianFaction</defName>
    <label>Salarian Settlers</label>
    <description>Following the implosion of their star, the salarian council moved some of the population onto this planet to colonize it. Because of a life presence scanner malfunction they didn't realize that the planet was occupied until they have already gotten here. A vote was struck to settle here after the strenuous journey they had just undergone. 
	The salarian residence here is quite new, but has spread tall and wide very quickly.</description>
